data.description: Gorgeous curb appeal invites you in! Entry showcases 11' coffered ceilings with tile extending throughout.  most of the home. Gorgeous wood floors thru-out. Kitchen with a wealth of cabinetry & granite counter space, travertine back splash, breakfast bar, stainless appliances & walk-in pantry. Primary Suite is spacious & boasts luxurious Primary Bathroom with double sinks, dual closets, mud-set shower & garden tub! Bedroom 2 is ensuite. Ceiling fans in all bedrooms, media room and the huge, covered patio! Get ready to move!!                                    One of the Seller is a licensed agent in Texas and Georgia.
